# Future Improvements

Recommended future work includes:

* Using U-Net or ResNet-based depth estimation
* Replacing FC point cloud prediction with geometric reprojection
* Using camera intrinsics for physically correct 3D reconstruction
* Increasing dataset size and training duration
* Adding advanced loss functions and point cloud regularization

Future pipeline recommendation:

```text
RGB → Depth Network → Geometric Projection → Pseudo LiDAR
```

This approach is expected to produce significantly better 3D reconstruction quality.
